c: 17
v: 1
t: "Ubutagatifu ni ubwa wawundi (Allah) wajyanye umugaragu we (Muhamadi) n’ijoro, amuvanye ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (wa Maka) akamujyana ku Musigiti wa Al Aq’sa (Umusigiti Mutagatifu w’i Yeruzalemu), twa- hundagaje imigisha impande zawo zose; (ibyo twabikoze) kugira ngo tumwereke bimwe mu bitangaza byacu. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Uwumva buri kintu, Ubona bihebuje"